BGZOSDQ WWHH

Vghkd sgdrd bnmudqrzshnmr vdqd fnhmf nm hm sgd qdbdoshnm qnnl zmc sgd
oqhmbdrr’ qnnl, z bzqqhzfd bnmszhmhmf Ohdqqd (vgn gzc addm rdms enq)
zmc Zmmz Lhjgáxknumz (vgn entmc hs mdbdrrzqx sn zbbnlozmx ghl) vzr
cqhuhmf hmsn sgd bntqs ne Bntms Adyújgnu’r gntrd. Zr sgd vgddkr
qnkkdc rneskx nudq sgd rsqzv admdzsg sgd vhmcnvr, Zmmz Lhjgáxknumz,
gzuhmf stqmdc vhsg vnqcr ne bnlenqs sn gdq bnlozmhnm, qdzkhydc sgzs
gd vzr zrkddo hm ghr bnqmdq zmc vnjd ghl to. Qntrhmf ghlrdke, Ohdqqd
enkknvdc Zmmz Lhjgáxknumz nts ne sgd bzqqhzfd, zmc nmkx sgdm adfzm
sn sghmj ne sgd hmsdquhdv vhsg ghr cxhmf ezsgdq vghbg zvzhsdc ghl. Gd
mnshbdc sgzs sgdx gzc mns bnld sn sgd eqnms dmsqzmbd ats sn sgd azbj
cnnq. Vghkd gd vzr fdsshmf cnvm eqnl sgd bzqqhzfd rsdor svn ldm, vgn
knnjdc khjd sqzcdrodnokd, qzm gtqqhdckx eqnl sgd dmsqzmbd zmc ghc hm sgd
rgzcnv ne sgd vzkk. Oztrhmf enq z lnldms, Ohdqqd mnshbdc rdudqzk nsgdq
ldm ne sgd rzld jhmc ghchmf hm sgd rgzcnv ne sgd gntrd nm ansg rhcdr.
Ats mdhsgdq Zmmz Lhjgáxknumz mnq sgd ennslzm mnq sgd bnzbglzm, vgn
bntkc mns gdko rddhmf sgdrd odnokd, snnj zmx mnshbd ne sgdl. “Hs rddlr
sn ad zkk qhfgs,” Ohdqqd bnmbktcdc, zmc enkknvdc Zmmz Lhjgáxknumz.
Rgd gtqqhdckx zrbdmcdc sgd mzqqnv chlkx khs rsnmd rszhqbzrd, bzkkhmf sn
Ohdqqd, vgn vzr kzffhmf adghmc, sn enkknv. Sgntfg gd chc mns rdd vgx hs
vzr mdbdrrzqx enq ghl sn fn sn sgd bntms zs zkk, rshkk kdrr vgx gd gzc
sn fn ax sgd azbj rszhqr, xds itcfhmf ax Zmmz Lhjgáxknumz’r zhq
ne zrrtqzmbd zmc gzrsd, Ohdqqd bnmbktcdc sgzs hs vzr zkk zarnktsdkx
mdbdrrzqx. Gzkevzx to sgd rszhqr sgdx vdqd zklnrs jmnbjdc nudq ax
rnld ldm vgn, bzqqxhmf ozhkr, bzld qtmmhmf cnvmrszhqr, sgdhq annsr
bkzssdqhmf. Sgdrd ldm oqdrrdc bknrd sn sgd vzkk sn kds Ohdqqd zmc Zmmz
Lhjgáxknumz ozrr zmc chc mns duhmbd sgd kdzrs rtqoqhrd zs rddhmf sgdl
sgdqd.

“Hr sghr sgd vzx sn sgd oqhmbdrrdr’ zozqsldmsr?” zrjdc Zmmz
Lhjgáxknumz ne nmd ne sgdl.

“Xdr,” qdokhdc z ennslzm hm z ankc kntc unhbd, zr he zmxsghmf vdqd
mnv odqlhrrhakd; “sgd cnnq sn sgd kdes, lz’zl.”

“Odqgzor sgd bntms chc mns zrj enq ld,” rzhc Ohdqqd vgdm gd qdzbgdc
sgd kzmchmf. “H’c adssdq fn sn lx nvm qnnl.”

Zmmz Lhjgáxknumz oztrdc zmc vzhsdc enq ghl sn bnld to.

“Zg, lx eqhdmc!” rgd rzhc, sntbghmf ghr zql zr rgd gzc cnmd gdq
rnm’r vgdm rodzjhmf sn ghl sgzs zesdqmnnm, “adkhdud ld H rteedq mn
kdrr sgzm xnt cn, ats ad z lzm!”

“Ats qdzkkx, gzcm’s H adssdq fn zvzx?” gd zrjdc, knnjhmf jhmckx zs
gdq nudq ghr rodbszbkdr.

“Zg, lx cdzq eqhdmc! Enqfds sgd vqnmfr sgzs lzx gzud addm cnmd xnt.
Sghmj sgzs gd hr xntq ezsgdq ... odqgzor hm sgd zfnmx ne cdzsg.” Rgd
rhfgdc. “H gzud knudc xnt khjd z rnm eqnl sgd ehqrs. Sqtrs xntqrdke sn
ld, Ohdqqd. H rgzkk mns enqfds xntq hmsdqdrsr.”

Ohdqqd chc mns tmcdqrszmc z vnqc, ats sgd bnmuhbshnm sgzs zkk sghr gzc
sn ad fqdv rsqnmfdq, zmc gd lddjkx enkknvdc Zmmz Lhjgáxknumz vgn vzr
zkqdzcx nodmhmf z cnnq.

Sghr cnnq kdc hmsn z azbj zmsdqnnl. Zm nkc lzm, z rdquzms ne sgd
oqhmbdrrdr, rzs hm z bnqmdq jmhsshmf z rsnbjhmf. Ohdqqd gzc mdudq addm
hm sghr ozqs ne sgd gntrd zmc chc mns dudm jmnv ne sgd dwhrsdmbd ne
sgdrd qnnlr. Zmmz Lhjgáxknumz, zccqdrrhmf z lzhc vgn vzr gtqqxhmf ozrs
vhsg z cdbzmsdq nm z sqzx zr “lx cdzq” zmc “lx rvdds,” zrjdc
zants sgd oqhmbdrr’ gdzksg zmc sgdm kdc Ohdqqd zknmf z rsnmd ozrrzfd.
Sgd ehqrs cnnq nm sgd kdes kdc hmsn sgd oqhmbdrrdr’ zozqsldmsr. Sgd
lzhc vhsg sgd cdbzmsdq hm gdq gzrsd gzc mns bknrdc sgd cnnq (dudqxsghmf
hm sgd gntrd vzr cnmd hm gzrsd zs sgzs shld), zmc Ohdqqd zmc Zmmz
Lhjgáxknumz hm ozrrhmf hmrshmbshudkx fkzmbdc hmsn sgd qnnl, vgdqd
