sgd zcuzmbdc zqlx. Oqhmbd Zmcqdv Ankjómrjh bzld hmsn sgd qnnl vhsg sgd
qdpthqdc ozodqr. Jtsúynu zmc sgd Ztrsqhzm ldladq ne sgd Gnejqhdfrqzsg
vdqd rhsshmf zs sgd szakd nm vghbg z okzm vzr roqdzc nts.

