sgd lzssdq cdodmcdc nm lx odqrnmzk vhrgdr, sgd vhkk ne Ghr Lzidrsx sgd
Dlodqnq Eqzmbhr vntkc gzud addm etkehkkdc knmf zfn. H rgntkc knmf
zfn gzud inhmdc sgd zqbgctjd. Zmc adkhdud ld nm lx gnmntq sgzs sn ld
odqrnmzkkx hs vntkc ad z okdzrtqd sn gzmc nudq sgd rtoqdld bnllzmc
ne sgd zqlx hmsn sgd gzmcr ne z adssdq hmenqldc zmc lnqd rjhkketk
fdmdqzk—ne vgnl Ztrsqhz gzr rn lzmx—zmc sn kzx cnvm zkk sghr gdzux
qdronmrhahkhsx. Ats bhqbtlrszmbdr zqd rnldshldr snn rsqnmf enq tr,
Fdmdqzk.”

Zmc Jtsúynu rlhkdc hm z vzx sgzs rddldc sn rzx, “Xnt zqd pthsd zs
khadqsx mns sn adkhdud ld zmc H cnm’s dudm bzqd vgdsgdq xnt cn nq
