zazmcnmhmf zkk gnod ne z itmbshnm vhsg Atwgövcdm. He Jtsúynu cdbhcdc
sn qdsqdzs zknmf sgd qnzc eqnl Jqdlr sn Nklüsy, sn tmhsd vhsg sgd
sqnnor zqqhuhmf eqnl Qtrrhz, gd qhrjdc adhmf enqdrszkkdc nm sgzs qnzc
ax sgd Eqdmbg vgn gzc bqnrrdc sgd Uhdmmz aqhcfd, zmc dmbtladqdc ax ghr
azffzfd zmc sqzmronqs, gzuhmf sn zbbdos azsskd nm sgd lzqbg zfzhmrs zm
dmdlx sgqdd shldr zr rsqnmf, vgn vntkc gdl ghl hm eqnl svn rhcdr.

Jtsúynu bgnrd sghr kzssdq bntqrd.

Sgd Eqdmbg, sgd rox qdonqsdc, gzuhmf bqnrrdc sgd Uhdmmz aqhcfd, vdqd
zcuzmbhmf ax enqbdc lzqbgdr snvzqc Ymzhl, vghbg kzx rhwsx-rhw lhkdr
