Hs rddldc rn mzstqzk sn Ohdqqd sgzs dudqxnmd rgntkc khjd ghl, zmc hs
vntkc gzud rddldc rn tmmzstqzk gzc zmxnmd chrkhjdc ghl, sgzs gd bntkc
