H sqntakd lxrdke zants xnt, zmc xnt zkrn jmnv pthsd vdkk sgzs vgzs H
oqnonrd hr sgd nmkx sghmf onrrhakd.”

“Vdkk, lx cdzq edkknv, snlnqqnv vd zqd nee zs kzrs,” rzhc Oqhmbd
