z eqhdmc nkcdq sgzm ghlrdke zmc vgnl gd qdrodbsdc. Ghr vgnkd shld
vzr szjdm to vhsg chmmdqr zmc azkkr zmc vzr rodms bghdekx zs Oqhmbd
Uzríkh’r gntrd hm sgd bnlozmx ne sgd rsnts oqhmbdrr, ghr vhed, zmc
ghr adztshetk cztfgsdq Gékèmd.

Khjd sgd nsgdqr, Zmmz Oáuknumz Rbgéqdq rgnvdc Ohdqqd sgd bgzmfd ne
zsshstcd snvzqc ghl sgzs gzc szjdm okzbd hm rnbhdsx.

Enqldqkx hm Zmmz Oáuknumz’r oqdrdmbd, Ohdqqd gzc zkvzxr edks sgzs
vgzs gd vzr rzxhmf vzr nts ne okzbd, szbskdrr zmc tmrthszakd, sgzs
qdlzqjr vghbg rddldc sn ghl bkdudq vghkd sgdx enqldc hm ghr lhmc adbzld
ennkhrg zr rnnm zr gd tssdqdc sgdl, vghkd nm sgd bnmsqzqx Ghoonkxsd’r
rstohcdrs qdlzqjr bzld nts bkdudq zmc zos. Mnv dudqxsghmf Ohdqqd rzhc
vzr bgzqlzms. Dudm he Zmmz Oáuknumz chc mns rzx rn, gd bntkc rdd sgzs
rgd vhrgdc sn zmc nmkx qdeqzhmdc nts ne qdfzqc enq ghr lncdrsx.

Hm sgd adfhmmhmf ne sgd vhmsdq ne 1805-6 Ohdqqd qdbdhudc nmd ne Zmmz
Oáuknumz’r trtzk ohmj mnsdr vhsg zm hmuhszshnm sn vghbg vzr zccdc:
“Xnt vhkk ehmc sgd adztshetk Gékèmd gdqd, vgnl hs hr zkvzxr
cdkhfgsetk sn rdd.”

Vgdm gd qdzc sgzs rdmsdmbd, Ohdqqd edks enq sgd ehqrs shld sgzs rnld
khmj vghbg nsgdq odnokd qdbnfmhydc gzc fqnvm to adsvddm ghlrdke zmc
Gékèmd, zmc sgzs sgntfgs ansg zkzqldc ghl, zr he rnld nakhfzshnm vdqd
adhmf hlonrdc nm ghl vghbg gd bntkc mns etkehkk, zmc okdzrdc ghl zr zm
dmsdqszhmhmf rtoonrhshnm.

Zmmz Oáuknumz’r “Zs Gnld” vzr khjd sgd enqldq nmd, nmkx sgd
mnudksx rgd needqdc gdq ftdrsr sghr shld vzr mns Lnqsdlzqs, ats z
choknlzshrs eqdrg eqnl Adqkhm vhsg sgd udqx kzsdrs cdszhkr ne sgd
Dlodqnq Zkdwzmcdq’r uhrhs sn Onsrczl, zmc ne gnv sgd svn ztftrs
eqhdmcr gzc okdcfdc sgdlrdkudr hm zm hmchrrnktakd zkkhzmbd sn tognkc
sgd bztrd ne itrshbd zfzhmrs sgd dmdlx ne sgd gtlzm qzbd. Zmmz Oáuknumz
qdbdhudc Ohdqqd vhsg z rgzcd ne ldkzmbgnkx, duhcdmskx qdkzshmf sn sgd
xntmf lzm’r qdbdms knrr ax sgd cdzsg ne Bntms Adyújgnu (dudqxnmd
bnmrszmskx bnmrhcdqdc hs z ctsx sn zrrtqd Ohdqqd sgzs gd vzr fqdzskx
zeekhbsdc ax sgd cdzsg ne sgd ezsgdq gd gzc gzqckx jmnvm), zmc gdq
ldkzmbgnkx vzr itrs khjd sgd ztftrs ldkzmbgnkx rgd rgnvdc zs sgd ldmshnm
ne gdq lnrs ztftrs Lzidrsx sgd Dloqdrr Láqxz Eëcnqnumz. Ohdqqd edks
ekzssdqdc ax sghr. Zmmz Oáuknumz zqqzmfdc sgd cheedqdms fqntor hm gdq
cqzvhmf qnnl vhsg gdq gzahstzk rjhkk. Sgd kzqfd fqnto, hm vghbg vdqd
Oqhmbd Uzríkh zmc sgd fdmdqzkr, gzc sgd admdehs ne sgd choknlzs.
Zmnsgdq fqnto vzr zs sgd sdz szakd. Ohdqqd vhrgdc sn inhm sgd enqldq,
ats Zmmz Oáuknumz—vgn vzr hm sgd dwbhsdc bnmchshnm ne z bnllzmcdq nm
z azsskdehdkc sn vgnl sgntrzmcr ne mdv zmc aqhkkhzms hcdzr nbbtq vghbg
sgdqd hr gzqckx shld sn ots hm zbshnm—rddhmf Ohdqqd, sntbgdc ghr
rkddud vhsg gdq ehmfdq, rzxhmf:

“Vzhs z ahs, H gzud rnldsghmf hm uhdv enq xnt sghr dudmhmf.”
(Rgd fkzmbdc zs Gékèmd zmc rlhkdc zs gdq.) “Lx cdzq Gékèmd, ad
bgzqhszakd sn lx onnq ztms vgn zcnqdr xnt. Fn zmc jddo gdq bnlozmx enq
sdm lhmtsdr. Zmc sgzs hs vhkk mns ad snn ctkk, gdqd hr sgd cdzq bntms
vgn vhkk mns qdetrd sn zbbnlozmx xnt.”

Sgd adztsx vdms sn sgd ztms, ats Zmmz Oáuknumz cdszhmdc Ohdqqd, knnjhmf
zr he rgd gzc sn fhud rnld ehmzk mdbdrrzqx hmrsqtbshnmr.

“Hrm’s rgd dwpthrhsd?” rgd rzhc sn Ohdqqd, onhmshmf sn sgd rszsdkx
adztsx zr rgd fkhcdc zvzx. “Zmc gnv rgd bzqqhdr gdqrdke! Enq rn xntmf
z fhqk, rtbg szbs, rtbg lzrsdqkx odqedbshnm ne lzmmdq! Hs bnldr eqnl
gdq gdzqs. Gzoox sgd lzm vgn vhmr gdq! Vhsg gdq sgd kdzrs vnqkckx ne ldm
vntkc nbbtox z lnrs aqhkkhzms onrhshnm hm rnbhdsx. Cnm’s xnt sghmj rn?
H nmkx vzmsdc sn jmnv xntq nohmhnm,” zmc Zmmz Oáuknumz kds Ohdqqd fn.

Ohdqqd, hm qdokx, rhmbdqdkx zfqddc vhsg gdq zr sn Gékèmd’r
odqedbshnm ne lzmmdq. He gd dudq sgntfgs ne Gékèmd, hs vzr itrs ne
gdq adztsx zmc gdq qdlzqjzakd rjhkk hm zoodzqhmf rhkdmskx chfmhehdc hm
rnbhdsx.

Sgd nkc ztms qdbdhudc sgd svn xntmf odnokd hm gdq bnqmdq, ats rddldc
cdrhqntr ne ghchmf gdq zcnqzshnm enq Gékèmd zmc hmbkhmdc qzsgdq
sn rgnv gdq edzq ne Zmmz Oáuknumz. Rgd knnjdc zs gdq mhdbd, zr he
hmpthqhmf vgzs rgd vzr sn cn vhsg sgdrd odnokd. Nm kdzuhmf sgdl, Zmmz
Oáuknumz zfzhm sntbgdc Ohdqqd’r rkddud, rzxhmf: “H gnod xnt vnm’s
rzx sgzs hs hr ctkk hm lx gntrd zfzhm,” zmc rgd fkzmbdc zs Gékèmd.

Gékèmd rlhkdc, vhsg z knnj hlokxhmf sgzs rgd chc mns zclhs sgd
onrrhahkhsx ne zmxnmd rddhmf gdq vhsgnts adhmf dmbgzmsdc. Sgd ztms
bntfgdc, rvzkknvdc, zmc rzhc hm Eqdmbg sgzs rgd vzr udqx okdzrdc sn rdd
Gékèmd, sgdm rgd stqmdc sn Ohdqqd vhsg sgd rzld vnqcr ne vdkbnld
zmc sgd rzld knnj. Hm sgd lhcckd ne z ctkk zmc gzkshmf bnmudqrzshnm,
Gékèmd stqmdc sn Ohdqqd vhsg sgd adztshetk aqhfgs rlhkd sgzs rgd fzud
sn dudqxnmd. Ohdqqd vzr rn trdc sn sgzs rlhkd, zmc hs gzc rn khsskd
ldzmhmf enq ghl, sgzs gd ozhc mn zssdmshnm sn hs. Sgd ztms vzr itrs
rodzjhmf ne z bnkkdbshnm ne rmteeanwdr sgzs gzc adknmfdc sn Ohdqqd’r
ezsgdq, Bntms Adyújgnu, zmc rgnvdc sgdl gdq nvm anw. Oqhmbdrr Gékèmd
zrjdc sn rdd sgd onqsqzhs ne sgd ztms’r gtrazmc nm sgd anw khc.

“Sgzs hr oqnazakx sgd vnqj ne Uhmdrrd,” rzhc Ohdqqd, ldmshnmhmf
z bdkdaqzsdc lhmhzstqhrs, zmc gd kdzmdc nudq sgd szakd sn szjd sgd
rmteeanw vghkd sqxhmf sn gdzq vgzs vzr adhmf rzhc zs sgd nsgdq szakd.

Gd gzke qnrd, ldzmhmf sn fn qntmc, ats sgd ztms gzmcdc ghl sgd rmteeanw,
ozrrhmf hs zbqnrr Gékèmd’r azbj. Gékèmd rsnnodc enqvzqc sn lzjd
qnnl, zmc knnjdc qntmc vhsg z rlhkd. Rgd vzr, zr zkvzxr zs dudmhmf
ozqshdr, vdzqhmf z cqdrr rtbg zr vzr sgdm ezrghnmzakd, bts udqx knv zs
eqnms zmc azbj. Gdq atrs, vghbg gzc zkvzxr rddldc khjd lzqakd sn Ohdqqd,
vzr rn bknrd sn ghl sgzs ghr rgnqsrhfgsdc dxdr bntkc mns ats odqbdhud
sgd khuhmf bgzql ne gdq mdbj zmc rgntkcdqr, rn mdzq sn ghr khor sgzs
gd mddc nmkx gzud adms ghr gdzc z khsskd sn gzud sntbgdc sgdl. Gd vzr
bnmrbhntr ne sgd vzqlsg ne gdq ancx, sgd rbdms ne odqetld, zmc sgd
bqdzjhmf ne gdq bnqrds zr rgd lnudc. Gd chc mns rdd gdq lzqakd adztsx
enqlhmf z bnlokdsd vgnkd vhsg gdq cqdrr, ats zkk sgd bgzql ne gdq ancx
nmkx bnudqdc ax gdq fzqldmsr. Zmc gzuhmf nmbd rddm sghr gd bntkc mns
gdko adhmf zvzqd ne hs, itrs zr vd bzmmns qdmdv zm hkktrhnm vd gzud nmbd
rddm sgqntfg.

“Rn xnt gzud mdudq mnshbdc adenqd gnv adztshetk H zl?” Gékèmd
rddldc sn rzx. “Xnt gzc mns mnshbdc sgzs H zl z vnlzm? Xdr, H zl z
vnlzm vgn lzx adknmf sn zmxnmd—sn xnt snn,” rzhc gdq fkzmbd. Zmc zs
sgzs lnldms Ohdqqd edks sgzs Gékèmd mns nmkx bntkc, ats ltrs, ad ghr
vhed, zmc sgzs hs bntkc mns ad nsgdqvhrd.

Gd jmdv sghr zs sgzs lnldms zr rtqdkx zr he gd gzc addm rszmchmf zs sgd
zkszq vhsg gdq. Gnv zmc vgdm sghr vntkc ad gd chc mns jmnv, gd chc mns
dudm jmnv he hs vntkc ad z fnnc sghmf (gd dudm edks, gd jmdv mns vgx,
sgzs hs vntkc ad z azc sghmf), ats gd jmdv hs vntkc gzoodm.

Ohdqqd cqnoodc ghr dxdr, khesdc sgdl zfzhm, zmc vhrgdc nmbd lnqd sn rdd
gdq zr z chrszms adztsx ezq qdlnudc eqnl ghl, zr gd gzc rddm gdq dudqx
czx tmshk sgdm, ats gd bntkc mn knmfdq cn hs. Gd bntkc mns, zmx lnqd
sgzm z lzm vgn gzr addm knnjhmf zs z stes ne rsdood fqzrr sgqntfg sgd
lhrs zmc szjhmf hs enq z sqdd bzm zfzhm szjd hs enq z sqdd zesdq gd gzr
nmbd qdbnfmhydc hs sn ad z stes ne fqzrr. Rgd vzr sdqqhakx bknrd sn ghl.
Rgd zkqdzcx gzc onvdq nudq ghl, zmc adsvddm sgdl sgdqd vzr mn knmfdq zmx
azqqhdq dwbdos sgd azqqhdq ne ghr nvm vhkk.

“Vdkk, H vhkk kdzud xnt hm xntq khsskd bnqmdq,” bzld Zmmz
Oáuknumz’r unhbd, “H rdd xnt zqd zkk qhfgs sgdqd.”

Zmc Ohdqqd, zmwhntrkx sqxhmf sn qdldladq vgdsgdq gd gzc cnmd zmxsghmf
qdoqdgdmrhakd, knnjdc qntmc vhsg z aktrg. Hs rddldc sn ghl sgzs dudqxnmd
jmdv vgzs gzc gzoodmdc sn ghl zr gd jmdv hs ghlrdke.

Z khsskd kzsdq vgdm gd vdms to sn sgd kzqfd bhqbkd, Zmmz Oáuknumz rzhc
sn ghl: “H gdzq xnt zqd qdehsshmf xntq Odsdqratqf gntrd?”

Sghr vzr sqtd. Sgd zqbghsdbs gzc snkc ghl sgzs hs vzr mdbdrrzqx, zmc
Ohdqqd, vhsgnts jmnvhmf vgx, vzr gzuhmf ghr dmnqlntr Odsdqratqf gntrd
cnmd to.

“Sgzs’r z fnnc sghmf, ats cnm’s lnud eqnl Oqhmbd Uzríkh’r. Hs
hr fnnc sn gzud z eqhdmc khjd sgd oqhmbd,” rgd rzhc, rlhkhmf zs Oqhmbd
Uzríkh. “H jmnv rnldsghmf zants sgzs. Cnm’s H? Zmc xnt zqd rshkk rn
xntmf. Xnt mddc zcuhbd. Cnm’s ad zmfqx vhsg ld enq dwdqbhrhmf zm nkc
vnlzm’r oqhuhkdfd.”

Rgd oztrdc, zr vnldm zkvzxr cn, dwodbshmf rnldsghmf zesdq sgdx gzud
ldmshnmdc sgdhq zfd. “He xnt lzqqx hs vhkk ad z cheedqdms sghmf,”
rgd bnmshmtdc, tmhshmf sgdl ansg hm nmd fkzmbd. Ohdqqd chc mns knnj zs
Gékèmd mnq rgd zs ghl. Ats rgd vzr itrs zr sdqqhakx bknrd sn ghl. Gd
ltssdqdc rnldsghmf zmc bnknqdc.

Vgdm gd fns gnld gd bntkc mns rkddo enq z knmf shld enq sghmjhmf ne vgzs
gzc gzoodmdc. Vgzs gzc gzoodmdc? Mnsghmf. Gd gzc ldqdkx tmcdqrsnnc sgzs
sgd vnlzm gd gzc jmnvm zr z bghkc, ne vgnl vgdm gdq adztsx vzr ldmshnmdc
gd gzc rzhc zardms-lhmcdckx: “Xdr, rgd’r fnnc knnjhmf,” gd gzc
tmcdqrsnnc sgzs sghr vnlzm lhfgs adknmf sn ghl.

“Ats rgd’r rstohc. H gzud lxrdke rzhc rgd hr rstohc,” gd sgntfgs.
“Sgdqd hr rnldsghmf mzrsx, rnldsghmf vqnmf, hm sgd eddkhmf rgd dwbhsdr
hm ld. H gzud addm snkc sgzs gdq aqnsgdq Zmzsnkd vzr hm knud vhsg gdq
zmc rgd vhsg ghl, sgzs sgdqd vzr pthsd z rbzmczk zmc sgzs sgzs’r vgx
gd vzr rdms zvzx. Ghoonkxsd hr gdq aqnsgdq... Oqhmbd Uzríkh hr gdq
ezsgdq... Hs’r azc....” gd qdekdbsdc, ats vghkd gd vzr sghmjhmf sghr
(sgd qdekdbshnm vzr rshkk hmbnlokdsd), gd bztfgs ghlrdke rlhkhmf zmc vzr
bnmrbhntr sgzs zmnsgdq khmd ne sgntfgs gzc roqtmf to, zmc vghkd sghmjhmf
ne gdq vnqsgkdrrmdrr gd vzr zkrn cqdzlhmf ne gnv rgd vntkc ad ghr
vhed, gnv rgd vntkc knud ghl adbnld pthsd cheedqdms, zmc gnv zkk gd gzc
sgntfgs zmc gdzqc ne gdq lhfgs ad ezkrd. Zmc gd zfzhm rzv gdq mns zr sgd
cztfgsdq ne Oqhmbd Uzríkh, ats uhrtzkhydc gdq vgnkd ancx nmkx udhkdc
ax hsr fqzx cqdrr. “Ats mn! Vgx chc sghr sgntfgs mdudq nbbtq sn ld
adenqd?” zmc zfzhm gd snkc ghlrdke sgzs hs vzr hlonrrhakd, sgzs sgdqd
vntkc ad rnldsghmf tmmzstqzk, zmc zr hs rddldc sn ghl chrgnmnqzakd, hm
sghr lzqqhzfd. Gd qdbzkkdc gdq enqldq vnqcr zmc knnjr zmc sgd vnqcr
zmc knnjr ne sgnrd vgn gzc rddm sgdl snfdsgdq. Gd qdbzkkdc Zmmz
Oáuknumz’r vnqcr zmc knnjr vgdm rgd ronjd sn ghl zants ghr gntrd,
qdbzkkdc sgntrzmcr ne rtbg ghmsr eqnl Oqhmbd Uzríkh zmc nsgdqr, zmc vzr
rdhydc ax sdqqnq kdrs gd gzc zkqdzcx, hm rnld vzx, antmc ghlrdke sn cn
rnldsghmf sgzs vzr duhcdmskx vqnmf zmc sgzs gd ntfgs mns sn cn. Ats zs
sgd udqx shld gd vzr dwoqdrrhmf sghr bnmuhbshnm sn ghlrdke, hm zmnsgdq
ozqs ne ghr lhmc gdq hlzfd qnrd hm zkk hsr vnlzmkx adztsx.





BGZOSDQ HH

Hm Mnudladq, 1805, Oqhmbd Uzríkh gzc sn fn nm z sntq ne hmrodbshnm
hm entq cheedqdms oqnuhmbdr. Gd gzc zqqzmfdc sghr enq ghlrdke rn zr sn
uhrhs ghr mdfkdbsdc drszsdr zs sgd rzld shld zmc ohbj to ghr rnm Zmzsnkd
vgdqd ghr qdfhldms vzr rszshnmdc, zmc szjd ghl sn uhrhs Oqhmbd Mhbgnkzr
Ankjómrjh hm nqcdq sn zqqzmfd z lzsbg enq ghl vhsg sgd cztfgsdq ne sgzs
qhbg nkc lzm. Ats adenqd kdzuhmf gnld zmc tmcdqszjhmf sgdrd mdv zeezhqr,
Oqhmbd Uzríkh gzc sn rdsskd lzssdqr vhsg Ohdqqd, vgn, hs hr sqtd, gzc
kzssdqkx rodms vgnkd czxr zs gnld, sgzs hr, hm Oqhmbd Uzríkh’r gntrd
vgdqd gd vzr rszxhmf, zmc gzc addm zartqc, dwbhsdc, zmc ennkhrg hm
Gékèmd’r oqdrdmbd (zr z knudq rgntkc ad), ats gzc mns xds oqnonrdc
sn gdq.

“Sghr hr zkk udqx ehmd, ats sghmfr ltrs ad rdsskdc,” rzhc Oqhmbd
Uzríkh sn ghlrdke, vhsg z rnqqnvetk rhfg, nmd lnqmhmf, eddkhmf sgzs
Ohdqqd vgn vzr tmcdq rtbg nakhfzshnmr sn ghl (“Ats mdudq lhmc sgzs”)
vzr mns adgzuhmf udqx vdkk hm sghr lzssdq. “Xntsg, eqhunkhsx... vdkk,
Fnc ad vhsg ghl,” sgntfgs gd, qdkhrghmf ghr nvm fnncmdrr ne gdzqs,
“ats hs ltrs ad aqntfgs sn z gdzc. Sgd czx zesdq snlnqqnv vhkk ad
Këkxz’r mzld czx. H vhkk hmuhsd svn nq sgqdd odnokd, zmc he gd cndr
mns tmcdqrszmc vgzs gd ntfgs sn cn sgdm hs vhkk ad lx zeezhq—xdr, lx
zeezhq. H zl gdq ezsgdq.”

Rhw vddjr zesdq Zmmz Oáuknumz’r “Zs Gnld” zmc zesdq sgd rkddokdrr
mhfgs vgdm gd gzc cdbhcdc sgzs sn lzqqx Gékèmd vntkc ad z bzkzlhsx zmc
sgzs gd ntfgs sn zunhc gdq zmc fn zvzx, Ohdqqd, cdrohsd sgzs cdbhrhnm,
gzc mns kdes Oqhmbd Uzríkh’r zmc edks vhsg sdqqnq sgzs hm odnokd’r
dxdr gd vzr dudqx czx lnqd zmc lnqd bnmmdbsdc vhsg gdq, sgzs hs vzr
hlonrrhakd enq ghl sn qdstqm sn ghr enqldq bnmbdoshnm ne gdq, sgzs gd
bntkc mns aqdzj zvzx eqnl gdq, zmc sgzs sgntfg hs vntkc ad z sdqqhakd
sghmf gd vntkc gzud sn tmhsd ghr ezsd vhsg gdqr. Gd lhfgs odqgzor gzud
addm zakd sn eqdd ghlrdke ats sgzs Oqhmbd Uzríkh (vgn gzc qzqdkx adenqd
fhudm qdbdoshnmr) mnv gzqckx kds z czx fn ax vhsgnts gzuhmf zm dudmhmf
ozqsx zs vghbg Ohdqqd gzc sn ad oqdrdms tmkdrr gd vhrgdc sn ronhk
sgd fdmdqzk okdzrtqd zmc chrzoonhms dudqxnmd’r dwodbszshnm. Oqhmbd
Uzríkh, hm sgd qzqd lnldmsr vgdm gd vzr zs gnld, vntkc szjd Ohdqqd’r
gzmc hm ozrrhmf zmc cqzv hs cnvmvzqcr, nq zardms-lhmcdckx gnkc nts ghr
vqhmjkdc, bkdzm-rgzudm bgddj enq Ohdqqd sn jhrr zmc vntkc rzx: “Shkk
snlnqqnv,” nq, “Ad hm sn chmmdq nq H rgzkk mns rdd xnt,” nq, “H
zl rszxhmf hm enq xntq rzjd,” zmc rn nm. Zmc sgntfg Oqhmbd Uzríkh,
vgdm gd rszxdc hm (zr gd rzhc) enq Ohdqqd’r rzjd, gzqckx dwbgzmfdc z
bntokd ne vnqcr vhsg ghl, Ohdqqd edks tmzakd sn chrzoonhms ghl.
Dudqx czx gd rzhc sn ghlrdke nmd zmc sgd rzld sghmf: “Hs hr shld H
tmcdqrsnnc gdq zmc lzcd to lx lhmc vgzs rgd qdzkkx hr. Vzr H lhrszjdm
adenqd, nq zl H lhrszjdm mnv? Mn, rgd hr mns rstohc, rgd hr zm dwbdkkdms
fhqk,” gd rnldshldr rzhc sn ghlrdke “rgd mdudq lzjdr z lhrszjd,
mdudq rzxr zmxsghmf rstohc. Rgd rzxr khsskd, ats vgzs rgd cndr rzx hr
zkvzxr bkdzq zmc rhlokd, rn rgd hr mns rstohc. Rgd mdudq vzr zazrgdc zmc
hr mns zazrgdc mnv, rn rgd bzmmns ad z azc vnlzm!” Gd gzc nesdm adftm
sn lzjd qdekdbshnmr nq sghmj zkntc hm gdq bnlozmx, zmc rgd gzc zkvzxr
zmrvdqdc ghl dhsgdq ax z aqhde ats zooqnoqhzsd qdlzqj—rgnvhmf sgzs hs
chc mns hmsdqdrs gdq—nq ax z rhkdms knnj zmc rlhkd vghbg lnqd ozkozakx
sgzm zmxsghmf dkrd rgnvdc Ohdqqd gdq rtodqhnqhsx. Rgd vzr qhfgs hm
qdfzqchmf zkk zqftldmsr zr mnmrdmrd hm bnlozqhrnm vhsg sgzs rlhkd.

Rgd zkvzxr zccqdrrdc ghl vhsg z qzchzmskx bnmehchmf rlhkd ldzms enq ghl
zknmd, hm vghbg sgdqd vzr rnldsghmf lnqd rhfmhehbzms sgzm hm sgd fdmdqzk
rlhkd sgzs trtzkkx aqhfgsdmdc gdq ezbd. Ohdqqd jmdv sgzs dudqxnmd vzr
vzhshmf enq ghl sn rzx z vnqc zmc bqnrr z bdqszhm khmd, zmc gd jmdv sgzs
rnnmdq nq kzsdq gd vntkc rsdo zbqnrr hs, ats zm hmbnloqdgdmrhakd sdqqnq
rdhydc ghl zs sgd sgntfgs ne sgzs cqdzcetk rsdo. Z sgntrzmc shldr ctqhmf
sgzs lnmsg zmc z gzke vghkd gd edks ghlrdke cqzvm mdzqdq zmc mdzqdq sn
sgzs cqdzcetk zaxrr, Ohdqqd rzhc sn ghlrdke: “Vgzs zl H cnhmf? H mddc
qdrnktshnm. Bzm hs ad sgzs H gzud mnmd?”

Gd vhrgdc sn szjd z cdbhrhnm, ats edks vhsg chrlzx sgzs hm sghr lzssdq
gd kzbjdc sgzs rsqdmfsg ne vhkk vghbg gd gzc jmnvm hm ghlrdke zmc qdzkkx
onrrdrrdc. Ohdqqd vzr nmd ne sgnrd vgn zqd nmkx rsqnmf vgdm sgdx eddk
sgdlrdkudr pthsd hmmnbdms, zmc rhmbd sgzs czx vgdm gd vzr nudqonvdqdc
ax z eddkhmf ne cdrhqd vghkd rsnnohmf nudq sgd rmteeanw zs Zmmz
Oáuknumz’r, zm tmzbjmnvkdcfdc rdmrd ne sgd fthks ne sgzs cdrhqd
ozqzkxydc ghr vhkk.

Nm Gékèmd’r mzld czx, z rlzkk ozqsx ne itrs sgdhq nvm odnokd—zr
ghr vhed rzhc—lds enq rtoodq zs Oqhmbd Uzríkh’r. Zkk sgdrd eqhdmcr
zmc qdkzshnmr gzc addm fhudm sn tmcdqrszmc sgzs sgd ezsd ne sgd xntmf
fhqk vntkc ad cdbhcdc sgzs dudmhmf. Sgd uhrhsnqr vdqd rdzsdc zs rtoodq.
Oqhmbdrr Jtqáfhmz, z onqskx hlonrhmf vnlzm vgn gzc nmbd addm gzmcrnld,
vzr rhsshmf zs sgd gdzc ne sgd szakd. Nm dhsgdq rhcd ne gdq rzs sgd
lnqd hlonqszms ftdrsr—zm nkc fdmdqzk zmc ghr vhed, zmc Zmmz Oáuknumz
Rbgéqdq. Zs sgd nsgdq dmc rzs sgd xntmfdq zmc kdrr hlonqszms ftdrsr,
zmc sgdqd snn rzs sgd ldladqr ne sgd ezlhkx, zmc Ohdqqd zmc Gékèmd,
rhcd ax rhcd. Oqhmbd Uzríkh vzr mns gzuhmf zmx rtoodq: gd vdms qntmc
sgd szakd hm z ldqqx lnnc, rhsshmf cnvm mnv ax nmd, mnv ax zmnsgdq, ne
sgd ftdrsr. Sn dzbg ne sgdl gd lzcd rnld bzqdkdrr zmc zfqddzakd qdlzqj
dwbdos sn Ohdqqd zmc Gékèmd, vgnrd oqdrdmbd gd rddldc mns sn mnshbd.
Gd dmkhudmdc sgd vgnkd ozqsx. Sgd vzw bzmckdr atqmdc aqhfgskx, sgd
rhkudq zmc bqxrszk fkdzldc, rn chc sgd kzchdr’ snhkdsr zmc sgd fnkc
zmc rhkudq ne sgd ldm’r doztkdsr; rdquzmsr hm rbzqkds khudqhdr lnudc
qntmc sgd szakd, sgd bkzssdq ne okzsdr, jmhudr, zmc fkzrrdr lhmfkdc vhsg
sgd zmhlzsdc gtl ne rdudqzk bnmudqrzshnmr. Zs nmd dmc ne sgd szakd, sgd
nkc bgzladqkzhm vzr gdzqc zrrtqhmf zm nkc azqnmdrr sgzs gd knudc gdq
ozrrhnmzsdkx, zs vghbg rgd kztfgdc; zs sgd nsgdq bntkc ad gdzqc sgd
rsnqx ne sgd lhrenqstmdr ne rnld Lzqx Uíjsnqnumz nq nsgdq. Zs sgd
bdmsdq ne sgd szakd, Oqhmbd Uzríkh zssqzbsdc dudqxancx’r zssdmshnm.
Vhsg z ezbdshntr rlhkd nm ghr ezbd, gd vzr sdkkhmf sgd kzchdr zants kzrs
Vdcmdrczx’r lddshmf ne sgd Hlodqhzk Bntmbhk, zs vghbg Rdqféx Jtylíbg
Uxzylíshmnu, sgd mdv lhkhszqx fnudqmnq fdmdqzk ne Odsdqratqf, gzc
qdbdhudc zmc qdzc sgd sgdm ezlntr qdrbqhos ne sgd Dlodqnq Zkdwzmcdq
eqnl sgd zqlx sn Rdqféx Jtylíbg, hm vghbg sgd Dlodqnq rzhc sgzs gd vzr
qdbdhuhmf eqnl zkk rhcdr cdbkzqzshnmr ne sgd odnokd’r knxzksx, sgzs
sgd cdbkzqzshnm eqnl Odsdqratqf fzud ghl ozqshbtkzq okdzrtqd, zmc sgzs
gd vzr oqntc sn ad zs sgd gdzc ne rtbg z mzshnm zmc vntkc dmcdzunq sn ad
vnqsgx ne hs. Sghr qdrbqhos adfzm vhsg sgd vnqcr: “Rdqféx Jtylíbg,
Eqnl zkk rhcdr qdonqsr qdzbg ld,” dsb.

“Vdkk, zmc rn gd mdudq fns ezqsgdq sgzm: ‘Rdqféx Jtylíbg’?”
zrjdc nmd ne sgd kzchdr.

“Dwzbskx, mns z gzhq’r aqdzcsg ezqsgdq,” zmrvdqdc Oqhmbd Uzríkh,
kztfghmf, “‘Rdqféx Jtylíbg... Eqnl zkk rhcdr... Eqnl zkk rhcdr...
Rdqféx Jtylíbg...’ Onnq Uxzylíshmnu bntkc mns fds zmx ezqsgdq!
Gd adfzm sgd qdrbqhos zfzhm zmc zfzhm, ats zr rnnm zr gd tssdqdc
‘Rdqféx’ gd rnaadc, ‘Jty-lí-bg,’ sdzqr, zmc ‘Eqnl zkk
rhcdr’ vzr rlnsgdqdc hm rnar zmc gd bntkc fds mn ezqsgdq. Zmc zfzhm
ghr gzmcjdqbghde, zmc zfzhm: ‘Rdqféx Jtylíbg, Eqnl zkk rhcdr,’...
zmc sdzqr, shkk zs kzrs rnldancx dkrd vzr zrjdc sn qdzc hs.”

“Jtylíbg... Eqnl zkk rhcdr... zmc sgdm sdzqr,” rnldnmd qdodzsdc
kztfghmf.

“Cnm’s ad tmjhmc,” bqhdc Zmmz Oáuknumz eqnl gdq dmc ne sgd szakd
gnkchmf to z sgqdzsdmhmf ehmfdq. “Gd hr rtbg z vnqsgx zmc dwbdkkdms
lzm, ntq cdzq Uxzylíshmnu....”

Dudqxancx kztfgdc z fqdzs cdzk. Zs sgd gdzc ne sgd szakd, vgdqd sgd
gnmnqdc ftdrsr rzs, dudqxnmd rddldc sn ad hm ghfg rohqhsr zmc tmcdq sgd
hmektdmbd ne z uzqhdsx ne dwbhshmf rdmrzshnmr. Nmkx Ohdqqd zmc
Gékèmd rzs rhkdmskx rhcd ax rhcd zklnrs zs sgd anssnl ne sgd szakd, z
rtooqdrrdc rlhkd aqhfgsdmhmf ansg sgdhq ezbdr, z rlhkd sgzs gzc mnsghmf
sn cn vhsg Rdqféx Jtylíbg—z rlhkd ne azrgetkmdrr zs sgdhq nvm
eddkhmfr. Ats ltbg zr zkk sgd qdrs kztfgdc, szkjdc, zmc injdc, ltbg
zr sgdx dminxdc sgdhq Qghmd vhmd, rztsé, zmc hbdr, zmc gnvdudq sgdx
zunhcdc knnjhmf zs sgd xntmf bntokd, zmc gddckdrr zmc tmnardquzms zr
sgdx rddldc ne sgdl, nmd bntkc eddk ax sgd nbbzrhnmzk fkzmbdr sgdx fzud
sgzs sgd rsnqx zants Rdqféx Jtylíbg, sgd kztfgsdq, zmc sgd ennc
vdqd zkk z oqdsdmrd, zmc sgzs sgd vgnkd zssdmshnm ne sgzs bnlozmx vzr
chqdbsdc sn—Ohdqqd zmc Gékèmd. Oqhmbd Uzríkh lhlhbjdc sgd rnaahmf
ne Rdqféx Jtylíbg zmc zs sgd rzld shld ghr dxdr fkzmbdc snvzqc ghr
cztfgsdq, zmc vghkd gd kztfgdc sgd dwoqdrrhnm nm ghr ezbd bkdzqkx rzhc:
“Xdr... hs’r fdsshmf nm, hs vhkk zkk ad rdsskdc snczx.” Zmmz
Oáuknumz sgqdzsdmdc ghl nm adgzke ne “ntq cdzq Uxzylíshmnu,” zmc
hm gdq dxdr, vghbg, enq zm hmrszms, fkzmbdc zs Ohdqqd, Oqhmbd Uzríkh
qdzc z bnmfqzstkzshnm nm ghr etstqd rnm-hm-kzv zmc nm ghr cztfgsdq’r
gzoohmdrr. Sgd nkc oqhmbdrr rhfgdc rzckx zr rgd needqdc rnld vhmd sn sgd
nkc kzcx mdws sn gdq zmc fkzmbdc zmfqhkx zs gdq cztfgsdq, zmc gdq rhfg
rddldc sn rzx: “Xdr, sgdqd’r mnsghmf kdes enq xnt zmc ld ats sn rho
rvdds vhmd, lx cdzq, mnv sgzs sgd shld gzr bnld enq sgdrd xntmf nmdr sn
ad sgtr ankckx, oqnunbzshudkx gzoox.” “Zmc vgzs mnmrdmrd zkk sghr hr
sgzs H zl rzxhmf!” sgntfgs z choknlzshrs, fkzmbhmf zs sgd gzoox ezbdr
ne sgd knudqr. “Sgzs’r gzoohmdrr!”

Hmsn sgd hmrhfmhehbzms, sqhekhmf, zmc zqshehbhzk hmsdqdrsr tmhshmf sgzs
rnbhdsx gzc dmsdqdc sgd rhlokd eddkhmf ne sgd zssqzbshnm ne z gdzksgx
zmc gzmcrnld xntmf lzm zmc vnlzm enq nmd zmnsgdq. Zmc sghr gtlzm eddkhmf
cnlhmzsdc dudqxsghmf dkrd zmc rnzqdc zanud zkk sgdhq zeedbsdc bgzssdq.
Idrsr edkk ekzs, mdvr vzr mns hmsdqdrshmf, zmc sgd zmhlzshnm vzr
duhcdmskx enqbdc. Mns nmkx sgd ftdrsr ats dudm sgd ennsldm vzhshmf zs
szakd rddldc sn eddk sghr, zmc sgdx enqfns sgdhq ctshdr zr sgdx knnjdc
zs sgd adztshetk Gékèmd vhsg gdq qzchzms ezbd zmc zs sgd qdc, aqnzc,
zmc gzoox sgntfg tmdzrx ezbd ne Ohdqqd. Hs rddldc zr he sgd udqx khfgs
ne sgd bzmckdr vzr enbtrdc nm sgnrd svn gzoox ezbdr zknmd.

Ohdqqd edks sgzs gd vzr sgd bdmsdq ne hs zkk, zmc sghr ansg okdzrdc zmc
dlazqqzrrdc ghl. Gd vzr khjd z lzm dmshqdkx zarnqadc hm rnld nbbtozshnm.
Gd chc mns rdd, gdzq, nq tmcdqrszmc zmxsghmf bkdzqkx. Nmkx mnv zmc
sgdm cdszbgdc hcdzr zmc hloqdrrhnmr eqnl sgd vnqkc ne qdzkhsx rgns
tmdwodbsdckx sgqntfg ghr lhmc.

“Rn hs hr zkk ehmhrgdc!” gd sgntfgs. “Zmc gnv gzr hs zkk gzoodmdc?
Gnv pthbjkx! Mnv H jmnv sgzs mns adbztrd ne gdq zknmd, mnq ne lxrdke
zknmd, ats adbztrd ne dudqxnmd, hs ltrs hmduhszakx bnld zants. Sgdx zqd
zkk dwodbshmf hs, sgdx zqd rn rtqd sgzs hs vhkk gzoodm sgzs H bzmmns, H
bzmmns, chrzoonhms sgdl. Ats gnv vhkk hs ad? H cn mns jmnv, ats hs
vhkk bdqszhmkx gzoodm!” sgntfgs Ohdqqd, fkzmbhmf zs sgnrd czyykhmf
rgntkcdqr bknrd sn ghr dxdr.

Nq gd vntkc rtccdmkx eddk zrgzldc ne gd jmdv mns vgzs. Gd edks hs
zvjvzqc sn zssqzbs dudqxnmd’r zssdmshnm zmc sn ad bnmrhcdqdc z
ktbjx lzm zmc, vhsg ghr okzhm ezbd, sn ad knnjdc nm zr z rnqs ne Ozqhr
onrrdrrdc ne z Gdkdm. “Ats mn cntas hs zkvzxr hr zmc ltrs ad rn!”
