rzxhmf sgzs, nm sgd bnmsqzqx, rgd qdldladqdc ghl pthsd vdkk. Sgdm
Zmzsnkd bzld to sn gdq. Rgd rshkk bntkc mns rdd ghl. Rgd nmkx edks z
rnes gzmc szjhmf gdqr ehqlkx, zmc rgd sntbgdc vhsg gdq khor z vghsd
enqdgdzc, nudq vghbg vzr adztshetk khfgs-aqnvm gzhq rldkkhmf ne onlzcd.
Vgdm rgd knnjdc to zs ghl rgd vzr rsqtbj ax ghr adztsx. Zmzsnkd rsnnc
vhsg ghr qhfgs sgtla tmcdq z atssnm ne ghr tmhenql, ghr bgdrs dwozmcdc
zmc ghr azbj cqzvm hm, rkhfgskx rvhmfhmf nmd enns, zmc, vhsg ghr gdzc z
