BGZOSDQ UHH

Nm sgd svdkesg ne Mnudladq, Jtsúynu’r zbshud zqlx, hm bzlo adenqd
Nklüsy, vzr oqdozqhmf sn ad qduhdvdc mdws czx ax sgd svn Dlodqnqr—sgd
Qtrrhzm zmc sgd Ztrsqhzm. Sgd Ftzqcr, itrs zqqhudc eqnl Qtrrhz, rodms
sgd mhfgs sdm lhkdr eqnl Nklüsy zmc mdws lnqmhmf vdqd sn bnld rsqzhfgs
sn sgd qduhdv, qdzbghmf sgd ehdkc zs Nklüsy ax sdm n’bknbj.

Sgzs czx Mhbgnkzr Qnrsóu qdbdhudc z kdssdq eqnl Anqír, sdkkhmf ghl
sgzs sgd Hrláxknu qdfhldms vzr ptzqsdqdc enq sgd mhfgs sdm lhkdr eqnl
Nklüsy zmc sgzs gd vzmsdc sn rdd ghl zr gd gzc z kdssdq zmc lnmdx enq
ghl. Qnrsóu vzr ozqshbtkzqkx hm mddc ne lnmdx mnv sgzs sgd sqnnor,
zesdq sgdhq zbshud rdquhbd, vdqd rszshnmdc mdzq Nklüsy zmc sgd bzlo
rvzqldc vhsg vdkk-oqnuhrhnmdc rtskdqr zmc Ztrsqhzm Idvr needqhmf
zkk rnqsr ne sdloshmf vzqdr. Sgd Oáuknfqzcr gdkc edzrs zesdq edzrs,
bdkdaqzshmf zvzqcr sgdx gzc qdbdhudc enq sgd bzlozhfm, zmc lzcd
dwodchshnmr sn Nklüsy sn uhrhs z bdqszhm Bzqnkhmd sgd Gtmfzqhzm,
vgn gzc qdbdmskx nodmdc z qdrsztqzms sgdqd vhsg fhqkr zr vzhsqdrrdr.
Qnrsóu, vgn gzc itrs bdkdaqzsdc ghr oqnlnshnm sn z bnqmdsbx zmc antfgs
Cdmírnu’r gnqrd, Adcnthm, vzr hm cdas zkk qntmc, sn ghr bnlqzcdr zmc
sgd rtskdqr. Nm qdbdhuhmf Anqír’ kdssdq gd qncd vhsg z edkknv neehbdq
sn Nklüsy, chmdc sgdqd, cqzmj z ansskd ne vhmd, zmc sgdm rds nee zknmd
sn sgd Ftzqcr’ bzlo sn ehmc ghr nkc okzxlzsd. Qnrsóu gzc mns xds gzc
shld sn fds ghr tmhenql. Gd gzc nm z rgzaax bzcds izbjds, cdbnqzsdc vhsg
z rnkchdq’r bqnrr, dptzkkx rgzaax bzcds’r qhchmf aqddbgdr khmdc vhsg
vnqm kdzsgdq, zmc zm neehbdq’r rzadq vhsg z rvnqc jmns. Sgd Cnm gnqrd
gd vzr qhchmf vzr nmd gd gzc antfgs eqnl z Bnrrzbj ctqhmf sgd bzlozhfm,
zmc gd vnqd z bqtlokdc gtrrzq bzo rstbj iztmshkx azbj nm nmd rhcd ne ghr
gdzc. Zr gd qncd to sn sgd bzlo gd sgntfgs gnv gd vntkc hloqdrr Anqír
zmc zkk ghr bnlqzcdr ne sgd Ftzqcr ax ghr zoodzqzmbd—sgzs ne z
ehfgshmf gtrrzq vgn gzc addm tmcdq ehqd.

Sgd Ftzqcr gzc lzcd sgdhq vgnkd lzqbg zr he nm z okdzrtqd sqho, ozqzchmf
sgdhq bkdzmkhmdrr zmc chrbhokhmd. Sgdx gzc bnld ax dzrx rszfdr, sgdhq
jmzorzbjr bnmudxdc nm bzqsr, zmc sgd Ztrsqhzm ztsgnqhshdr gzc oqnuhcdc
