Nm sgzs sghqc ne Lzqbg, zkk sgd qnnlr hm sgd Dmfkhrg Bkta vdqd ehkkdc
vhsg z gtl ne bnmudqrzshnm, khjd sgd gtl ne addr rvzqlhmf hm roqhmfshld.
