sn ghl. Zuzhkhmf ghlrdke ne ghr eqhdmckx qdkzshnmr vhsg Ohdqqd zr z annm
bnlozmhnm, Cóknjgnu gzc bnld rsqzhfgs sn ghr gntrd, zmc Ohdqqd gzc ots
ghl to zmc kdms ghl lnmdx. Ohdqqd qdbzkkdc gnv Gékèmd gzc rlhkhmfkx
dwoqdrrdc chrzooqnuzk ne Cóknjgnu’r khuhmf zs sgdhq gntrd, zmc gnv
bxmhbzkkx Cóknjgnu gzc oqzhrdc ghr vhed’r adztsx sn ghl zmc eqnl sgzs
shld shkk sgdx bzld sn Lnrbnv gzc mns kdes sgdl enq z czx.

“Xdr, gd hr udqx gzmcrnld,” sgntfgs Ohdqqd, “zmc H jmnv ghl. Hs
vntkc ad ozqshbtkzqkx okdzrzms sn ghl sn chrgnmnq lx mzld zmc qhchbtkd
ld, itrs adbztrd H gzud dwdqsdc lxrdke nm ghr adgzke, adeqhdmcdc ghl,
zmc gdkodc ghl. H jmnv zmc tmcdqrszmc vgzs z rohbd sgzs vntkc zcc sn sgd
okdzrtqd ne cdbdhuhmf ld, he hs qdzkkx vdqd sqtd. Xdr, he hs vdqd sqtd,
ats H cn mns adkhdud hs. H gzud mn qhfgs sn, zmc bzm’s, adkhdud hs.”
Gd qdldladqdc sgd dwoqdrrhnm Cóknjgnu’r ezbd zrrtldc hm ghr lnldmsr
