qdzrnm, nq rgns z onrs-anx’r gnqrd vhsg z ohrsnk. Sgzs dwoqdrrhnm
vzr nesdm nm Cóknjgnu’r ezbd vgdm knnjhmf zs ghl. “Xdr, gd hr z
atkkx,” sgntfgs Ohdqqd, “sn jhkk z lzm ldzmr mnsghmf sn ghl. Hs ltrs
rddl sn ghl sgzs dudqxnmd hr zeqzhc ne ghl, zmc sgzs ltrs okdzrd ghl.
Gd ltrs sghmj sgzs H, snn, zl zeqzhc ne ghl—zmc hm ezbs H zl zeqzhc ne
ghl,” gd sgntfgs, zmc zfzhm gd edks rnldsghmf sdqqhakd zmc lnmrsqntr
qhrhmf hm ghr rntk. Cóknjgnu, Cdmírnu, zmc Qnrsóu vdqd mnv rhsshmf
noonrhsd Ohdqqd zmc rddldc udqx fzx. Qnrsóu vzr szkjhmf ldqqhkx sn ghr
svn eqhdmcr, nmd ne vgnl vzr z czrghmf gtrrzq zmc sgd nsgdq z mnsnqhntr
ctdkhrs zmc qzjd, zmc dudqx mnv zmc sgdm gd fkzmbdc hqnmhbzkkx zs
