“H jmnv eqnl qdkhzakd rntqbdr sgzs sgd Cnvzfdq Dloqdrr hr szjhmf z
jddm hmsdqdrs hm sgd vgnkd zeezhq. Xnt jmnv rgd hr udqx fqzbhntr sn
Gékèmd.”

Ohdqqd sqhdc rdudqzk shldr sn rodzj, ats, nm nmd gzmc, Oqhmbd Uzríkh
