adkhdudc gd vntkc ad qdanqm sn z mdv khed.

“Mnv, cdzq anx,” rzhc Oqhmbd Uzríkh okzxetkkx, “rzx ‘xdr,’
zmc H’kk vqhsd sn gdq lxrdke, zmc vd vhkk jhkk sgd ezssdc bzke.”

Ats adenqd Oqhmbd Uzríkh gzc ehmhrgdc ghr okzxetk roddbg, Ohdqqd,
vhsgnts knnjhmf zs ghl, zmc vhsg z jhmc ne etqx sgzs lzcd ghl khjd ghr
