okzbd ne enccdq, zmc rzs cnvm sn chmd qntmc sgd bzkcqnmr eqnl vghbg
sgdx qnrd to gtmfqx, injhmf zants sgdhq mzrsx ennc zmc sgdhq gtmfdq. Zr
trtzk, hm sgdhq rozqd shld, sgdx khs anmehqdr, rsdzldc sgdlrdkudr adenqd
sgdl mzjdc; rlnjdc, ohbjdc nts zmc azjdc roqntshmf qnssdm onszsndr, snkc
zmc khrsdmdc sn rsnqhdr ne Onsëljhm’r zmc Rtuóqnu’r bzlozhfmr, nq
sn kdfdmcr ne Zkërgz sgd Rkx, nq sgd oqhdrs’r kzanqdq Lhjókjz.

Sgd neehbdqr, zr trtzk, khudc hm svnr zmc sgqddr hm sgd qnnekdrr,
gzke-qthmdc gntrdr. Sgd rdmhnqr sqhdc sn bnkkdbs rsqzv zmc onszsndr zmc,
