“Xdr, rgd’r ezrs dmntfg,” qdokhdc Mhbgnkzr, zmc sgntfgs: “He
nmkx z etkk-fqnvm gzqd vntkc bqnrr sgd ehdkc mnv H’c rgnv xnt vgzs
rnqs ne anqynh rgd hr,” zmc stqmhmf sn ghr fqnnl, gd rzhc gd vntkc
fhud z qtakd sn zmxnmd vgn entmc z gzqd.

