BGZOSDQ UHHH

Bntms Hkxá Qnrsóu gzc qdrhfmdc sgd onrhshnm ne Lzqrgzk ne sgd Mnahkhsx
adbztrd hs hmunkudc ghl hm snn ltbg dwodmrd, ats rshkk ghr zeezhqr
chc mns hloqnud. Mzsárgz zmc Mhbgnkzr nesdm mnshbdc sgdhq ozqdmsr
bnmedqqhmf snfdsgdq zmwhntrkx zmc oqhuzsdkx zmc gdzqc rtffdrshnmr ne
rdkkhmf sgd ehmd zmbdrsqzk Qnrsóu gntrd zmc drszsd mdzq Lnrbnv. Hs vzr
mns mdbdrrzqx sn dmsdqszhm rn eqddkx zr vgdm sgd bntms gzc addm Lzqrgzk,
zmc khed zs Nsqácmnd vzr pthdsdq sgzm hm enqldq xdzqr, ats rshkk sgd
dmnqlntr gntrd zmc hsr kncfdr vdqd etkk ne odnokd zmc lnqd sgzm svdmsx
rzs cnvm sn szakd dudqx czx. Sgdrd vdqd zkk sgdhq nvm odnokd vgn gzc
rdsskdc cnvm hm sgd gntrd zklnrs zr ldladqr ne sgd ezlhkx, nq odqrnmr
vgn vdqd, hs rddldc, nakhfdc sn khud hm sgd bntms’r gntrd. Rtbg vdqd
Chllkdq sgd ltrhbhzm zmc ghr vhed, Unfdk sgd czmbhmf lzrsdq zmc ghr
ezlhkx, Adkóuz, zm nkc lzhcdm kzcx, zm hmlzsd ne sgd gntrd, zmc lzmx
nsgdqr rtbg zr Oésxz’r stsnqr, sgd fhqkr’ enqldq fnudqmdrr, zmc
nsgdq odnokd vgn rhlokx entmc hs oqdedqzakd zmc lnqd zcuzmszfdntr sn
khud hm sgd bntms’r gntrd sgzm zs gnld. Sgdx gzc mns zr lzmx uhrhsnqr
