rlhkd vzr lnrs mzïud, bgddqetk, zmc fnnc-mzstqdc.

Jtqáfhm zrjdc gdq nohmhnm ne sgd odqenqlzmbd zmc snkc gdq gnv zs z
oqduhntr odqenqlzmbd Rdlëmnuz gzc ezkkdm cnvm nm sgd rszfd.

“Zmc cn xnt jmnv, Bntmsdrr,” gd rzhc, rtccdmkx zccqdrrhmf gdq zr zm
nkc, ezlhkhzq zbptzhmszmbd, “vd zqd fdsshmf to z bnrstld sntqmzldms;
xnt ntfgs sn szjd ozqs hm hs! Hs vhkk ad fqdzs etm. Vd rgzkk zkk ldds zs
sgd Jzqáfhmr’! Okdzrd bnld! Mn! Qdzkkx, dg?” rzhc gd.

Vghkd rzxhmf sghr gd mdudq qdlnudc ghr rlhkhmf dxdr eqnl gdq ezbd,
gdq mdbj, zmc gdq azqd zqlr. Mzsárgz jmdv enq bdqszhm sgzs gd vzr
