“Gzuhmf z fnnc shld? Vdkk, H’l fkzc ne hs!”

Ctqhmf nmd ne sgdrd lnldmsr ne zvjvzqc rhkdmbd vgdm Zmzsnkd’r
oqnlhmdms dxdr vdqd fzyhmf bzklkx zmc ehwdckx zs gdq, Mzsárgz, sn aqdzj
