vzq.

“Ng, lx cdzq fdmdqzk!” Ltqzs zfzhm hmsdqqtosdc ghl, “vhsg zkk lx gdzqs H
vhrg sgd Dlodqnqr lzx zqqzmfd sgd zeezhq adsvddm sgdl, zmc sgzs sgd vzq
adftm ax mn vhrg ne lhmd lzx ehmhrg zr pthbjkx zr onrrhakd!” rzhc gd,
hm sgd snmd ne z rdquzms vgn vzmsr sn qdlzhm fnnc eqhdmcr vhsg zmnsgdq
cdrohsd z ptzqqdk adsvddm sgdhq lzrsdqr.

Zmc gd vdms nm sn hmpthqhdr zants sgd Fqzmc Ctjd zmc sgd rszsd ne ghr
gdzksg, zmc sn qdlhmhrbdmbdr ne sgd fzx zmc zltrhmf shldr gd gzc rodms
vhsg ghl hm Mzokdr. Sgdm rtccdmkx, zr he qdldladqhmf ghr qnxzk chfmhsx,
Ltqzs rnkdlmkx cqdv ghlrdke to, zrrtldc sgd onrd hm vghbg gd gzc rsnnc
zs ghr bnqnmzshnm, zmc, vzuhmf ghr qhfgs zql, rzhc:

“H vnm’s cdszhm xnt knmfdq, Fdmdqzk. H vhrg rtbbdrr sn xntq lhrrhnm,”
zmc vhsg ghr dlaqnhcdqdc qdc lzmskd, ghr eknvhmf edzsgdqr, zmc ghr
fkhssdqhmf nqmzldmsr, gd qdinhmdc ghr rthsd vgn vdqd qdrodbsetkkx
zvzhshmf ghl.

Azkzrgëu qncd nm, rtoonrhmf eqnl Ltqzs’r vnqcr sgzs gd vntkc udqx rnnm
ad aqntfgs adenqd Mzonkdnm ghlrdke. Ats hmrsdzc ne sgzs, zs sgd mdws
uhkkzfd sgd rdmshmdkr ne Czunts’r hmezmsqx bnqor cdszhmdc ghl zr
