Lnrbnv azkkr.

“Cn, okdzrd, enq gdzudm’r rzjd, qdkhdud ld ne rnldsghmf!” rzhc sgd
bntqhdq. “H gzud z rzbjetk ne kdssdqr sn ozqdmsr.”

Zlnmf sgdrd kdssdqr vzr nmd eqnl Mhbgnkzr Qnrsóu sn ghr ezsgdq. Ohdqqd
snnj sgzs kdssdq, zmc Qnrsnobgím zkrn fzud ghl sgd Dlodqnq’r zoodzk sn
Lnrbnv, vghbg gzc itrs addm oqhmsdc, sgd kzrs zqlx nqcdqr, zmc ghr nvm
