Nm qdstqmhmf eqnl z rdbnmc hmrodbshnm ne sgd khmdr, Mzonkdnm qdlzqjdc:

“Sgd bgdrrldm zqd rds to, sgd fzld vhkk adfhm snlnqqnv!”

Gzuhmf nqcdqdc otmbg zmc rtllnmdc cd Adztrrds, gd adfzm sn szkj sn ghl
zants Ozqhr zmc zants rnld bgzmfdr gd ldzms sn lzjd hm sgd Dloqdrr’
