rds sn vnqj H rgzkk cn hs zr mn nmd dkrd bntkc, ats mnv H bzm idrs, zmc
sgd lnqd H idrs zmc sgd bzkldq H zl sgd lnqd sqzmpthk zmc bnmehcdms xnt
