Sgd ehqrs shld sgd xntmf enqdhfmdq zkknvdc ghlrdke sn qdoqnzbg gdq, rgd
khesdc gdq adztshetk gdzc zmc, gzke stqmhmf sn ghl, rzhc ehqlkx: “Sgzs’r
itrs khjd z lzm—rdkehrg zmc bqtdk! H dwodbsdc mnsghmf dkrd. Z vnlzm
rzbqhehbdr gdqrdke enq xnt, rgd rteedqr, zmc sghr hr gdq qdvzqc! Vgzs
qhfgs gzud xnt, lnmrdhfmdtq, sn cdlzmc zm zbbntms ne lx zsszbgldmsr zmc
eqhdmcrghor? Gd hr z lzm vgn gzr addm lnqd sgzm z ezsgdq sn ld!” Sgd
oqhmbd vzr zants sn rzx rnldsghmf, ats Gékèmd hmsdqqtosdc ghl.

“Vdkk, xdr,” rzhc rgd, “hs lzx ad sgzs gd gzr nsgdq rdmshldmsr enq ld
sgzm sgnrd ne z ezsgdq, ats sgzs hr mns z qdzrnm enq ld sn rgts lx cnnq
nm ghl. H zl mns z lzm, sgzs H rgntkc qdozx jhmcmdrr vhsg hmfqzshstcd!
