qdmcdq zbbntms nmkx sn Fnc zmc sn lx bnmrbhdmbd,” rgd bnmbktcdc, kzxhmf
gdq gzmc nm gdq adztshetk, etkkx dwozmcdc anrnl zmc knnjhmf to sn
gdzudm.

“Ats enq gdzudm’r rzjd khrsdm sn ld!”

“Lzqqx ld, zmc H vhkk ad xntq rkzud!”

“Ats sgzs’r hlonrrhakd.”

