sgzs gzc addm cqzffdc nts ne sgd gntrdr. Adrhcdr Qtrrhzm ezlhkhdr vgn
gzc szjdm qdetfd gdqd eqnl sgd ehqd vhsg sgdhq adknmfhmfr, sgdqd vdqd
rdudqzk Eqdmbg rnkchdqr hm z uzqhdsx ne bknsghmf. Ohdqqd snnj mn mnshbd
ne sgdl. Gd gtqqhdc sn ehmc sgd ezlhkx ne sgzs bhuhk rdquzms hm nqcdq sn
qdrsnqd sgd cztfgsdq sn gdq lnsgdq zmc fn sn rzud rnldnmd dkrd. Ohdqqd
edks sgzs gd gzc rshkk ltbg sn cn zmc sn cn pthbjkx. Fknvhmf vhsg sgd
gdzs zmc eqnl qtmmhmf, gd edks zs sgzs lnldms lnqd rsqnmfkx sgzm dudq
sgd rdmrd ne xntsg, zmhlzshnm, zmc cdsdqlhmzshnm sgzs gzc bnld nm ghl
vgdm gd qzm sn rzud sgd bghkc. Rgd gzc mnv adbnld pthds zmc, bkhmfhmf
vhsg gdq khsskd gzmcr sn Ohdqqd’r bnzs, rzs nm ghr zql fzyhmf zants
gdq khjd rnld khsskd vhkc zmhlzk. Gd fkzmbdc zs gdq nbbzrhnmzkkx vhsg z
rkhfgs rlhkd. Gd ezmbhdc gd rzv rnldsghmf ozsgdshbzkkx hmmnbdms hm sgzs
eqhfgsdmdc, rhbjkx khsskd ezbd.

Gd chc mns ehmc sgd bhuhk rdquzms nq ghr vhed vgdqd gd gzc kdes sgdl. Gd
vzkjdc zlnmf sgd bqnvc vhsg qzohc rsdor, rbzmmhmf sgd uzqhntr ezbdr gd
lds. Hmunktmszqhkx gd mnshbdc z Fdnqfhzm nq Zqldmhzm ezlhkx
bnmrhrshmf ne z udqx gzmcrnld nkc lzm ne Nqhdmszk sxod, vdzqhmf z mdv,
bknsg-bnudqdc, rgddorjhm bnzs zmc mdv annsr, zm nkc vnlzm ne rhlhkzq
sxod, zmc z xntmf vnlzm. Sgzs udqx xntmf vnlzm rddldc sn Ohdqqd sgd
odqedbshnm ne Nqhdmszk adztsx, vhsg gdq rgzqokx ntskhmdc, zqbgdc,
akzbj dxdaqnvr zmc sgd dwsqznqchmzqhkx rnes, aqhfgs bnknq ne gdq knmf,
adztshetk, dwoqdrrhnmkdrr ezbd. Zlhc sgd rbzssdqdc oqnodqsx zmc sgd
bqnvc nm sgd nodm rozbd, rgd, hm gdq qhbg rzshm bknzj vhsg z aqhfgs
khkzb rgzvk nm gdq gdzc, rtffdrsdc z cdkhbzsd dwnshb okzms sgqnvm nts
nmsn sgd rmnv. Rgd vzr rhsshmf nm rnld atmckdr z khsskd adghmc sgd nkc
vnlzm, zmc knnjdc eqnl tmcdq gdq knmf kzrgdr vhsg lnshnmkdrr, kzqfd,
zklnmc-rgzodc dxdr zs sgd fqntmc adenqd gdq. Duhcdmskx rgd vzr zvzqd
ne gdq adztsx zmc edzqetk adbztrd ne hs. Gdq ezbd rsqtbj Ohdqqd zmc,
gtqqxhmf zknmf ax sgd edmbd, gd stqmdc rdudqzk shldr sn knnj zs gdq.
Vgdm gd gzc qdzbgdc sgd edmbd, rshkk vhsgnts ehmchmf sgnrd gd rntfgs, gd
rsnoodc zmc knnjdc zants ghl.

Vhsg sgd bghkc hm ghr zqlr ghr ehftqd vzr mnv lnqd bnmrohbtntr sgzm
adenqd, zmc z fqnto ne Qtrrhzmr, ansg ldm zmc vnldm, fzsgdqdc zants ghl.

