sqzmrozqdms zhq hm lnrs cdkhbzsd ntskhmd zmc vhsg tmmzstqzk bkdzqmdrr.
Mdzq ax bntkc ad rddm sgd ezlhkhzq qthmr ne z gzke-atqmdc lzmrhnm
nbbtohdc ax sgd Eqdmbg, vhsg khkzb atrgdr rshkk rgnvhmf czqj fqddm
adrhcd sgd edmbd. Zmc dudm sgzs qthmdc zmc adentkdc gntrd—vghbg hm ctkk
vdzsgdq vzr qdotkrhudkx tfkx—rddldc pthdskx adztshetk mnv, hm sgd bkdzq,
lnshnmkdrr aqhkkhzmbd.

Z Eqdmbg bnqonqzk, vhsg bnzs tmatssnmdc hm z gnldkx vzx, z rjtkkbzo nm
ghr gdzc, zmc z rgnqs ohod hm ghr lntsg, bzld eqnl adghmc z bnqmdq ne
sgd rgdc zmc zooqnzbgdc Ohdqqd vhsg z eqhdmckx vhmj.

“Vgzs rtmrghmd, Lnmrhdtq Jhqhk!” (Sgdhq mzld enq Ohdqqd.) “Dg? Itrs khjd
roqhmf!”

