sgntfg vgdmdudq gd needqdc hs Ohdqqd zkvzxr cdbkhmdc hs.

“Sn ad nm sgd lzqbg hm rtbg vdzsgdq...” gd adfzm.

Ohdqqd hmpthqdc vgzs vzr adhmf rzhc zants kdzuhmf, zmc sgd bnqonqzk snkc
