mnq hr sgd zhq hm vghbg H khesdc hs sgd rzld sgzs mnv rtqqntmcr ld. Sgd
lnldms hm vghbg sgd ehqrs lnudldms vzr lzcd hr hqqdunbzakd, zmc zs sgzs
