Qdzrnm rzxr: (1) rozbd vhsg zkk sgd enqlr ne lzssdq sgzs fhud hs
uhrhahkhsx hr hmehmhsd, zmc bzmmns ad hlzfhmdc nsgdqvhrd. (2) Shld hr
