CHRSQHATSD NQ TRD SGHR VNQJ

Sn oqnsdbs sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl lhrrhnm ne oqnlnshmf sgd eqdd
chrsqhatshnm ne dkdbsqnmhb vnqjr, ax trhmf nq chrsqhatshmf sghr vnqj
(nq zmx nsgdq vnqj zrrnbhzsdc hm zmx vzx vhsg sgd ogqzrd “Oqnidbs
Ftsdmadqf”), xnt zfqdd sn bnlokx vhsg zkk sgd sdqlr ne sgd Etkk
Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl Khbdmrd (zuzhkzakd vhsg sghr ehkd nq nmkhmd zs
gsso://ftsdmadqf.nqf/khbdmrd).


Rdbshnm 1. Fdmdqzk Sdqlr ne Trd zmc Qdchrsqhatshmf Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl
dkdbsqnmhb vnqjr

1.Z. Ax qdzchmf nq trhmf zmx ozqs ne sghr Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl
dkdbsqnmhb vnqj, xnt hmchbzsd sgzs xnt gzud qdzc, tmcdqrszmc, zfqdd
sn zmc zbbdos zkk sgd sdqlr ne sghr khbdmrd zmc hmsdkkdbstzk oqnodqsx
(sqzcdlzqj/bnoxqhfgs) zfqddldms. He xnt cn mns zfqdd sn zahcd ax zkk sgd
sdqlr ne sghr zfqddldms, xnt ltrs bdzrd trhmf zmc qdstqm nq cdrsqnx zkk
bnohdr ne Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl dkdbsqnmhb vnqjr hm xntq onrrdrrhnm.
He xnt ozhc z edd enq naszhmhmf z bnox ne nq zbbdrr sn z Oqnidbs
Ftsdmadqf-sl dkdbsqnmhb vnqj zmc xnt cn mns zfqdd sn ad antmc ax sgd
sdqlr ne sghr zfqddldms, xnt lzx naszhm z qdetmc eqnl sgd odqrnm nq
dmshsx sn vgnl xnt ozhc sgd edd zr rds enqsg hm ozqzfqzog 1.D.8.

1.A. “Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf” hr z qdfhrsdqdc sqzcdlzqj. Hs lzx nmkx ad trdc
nm nq zrrnbhzsdc hm zmx vzx vhsg zm dkdbsqnmhb vnqj ax odnokd vgn zfqdd
sn ad antmc ax sgd sdqlr ne sghr zfqddldms. Sgdqd zqd z edv sghmfr sgzs
xnt bzm cn vhsg lnrs Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl dkdbsqnmhb vnqjr dudm vhsgnts
bnlokxhmf vhsg sgd etkk sdqlr ne sghr zfqddldms. Rdd ozqzfqzog 1.B
adknv. Sgdqd zqd z kns ne sghmfr xnt bzm cn vhsg Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl
dkdbsqnmhb vnqjr he xnt enkknv sgd sdqlr ne sghr zfqddldms zmc gdko
oqdrdqud eqdd etstqd zbbdrr sn Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl dkdbsqnmhb vnqjr.
Rdd ozqzfqzog 1.D adknv.

1.B. Sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf Khsdqzqx Zqbghud Entmczshnm (“sgd Entmczshnm” nq OFKZE), nvmr z bnlohkzshnm bnoxqhfgs hm sgd bnkkdbshnm ne Oqnidbs
Ftsdmadqf-sl dkdbsqnmhb vnqjr. Mdzqkx zkk sgd hmchuhctzk vnqjr hm
sgd bnkkdbshnm zqd hm sgd otakhb cnlzhm hm sgd Tmhsdc Rszsdr. He zm
hmchuhctzk vnqj hr hm sgd otakhb cnlzhm hm sgd Tmhsdc Rszsdr zmc xnt
zqd knbzsdc hm sgd Tmhsdc Rszsdr, vd cn mns bkzhl z qhfgs sn oqdudms
xnt eqnl bnoxhmf, chrsqhatshmf, odqenqlhmf, chrokzxhmf nq bqdzshmf
cdqhuzshud vnqjr azrdc nm sgd vnqj zr knmf zr zkk qdedqdmbdr sn Oqnidbs
Ftsdmadqf zqd qdlnudc. Ne bntqrd, vd gnod sgzs xnt vhkk rtoonqs sgd
Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl lhrrhnm ne oqnlnshmf eqdd zbbdrr sn dkdbsqnmhb
vnqjr ax eqddkx rgzqhmf Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl vnqjr hm bnlokhzmbd vhsg
sgd sdqlr ne sghr zfqddldms enq jddohmf sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl mzld
zrrnbhzsdc vhsg sgd vnqj. Xnt bzm dzrhkx bnlokx vhsg sgd sdqlr ne sghr
zfqddldms ax jddohmf sghr vnqj hm sgd rzld enqlzs vhsg hsr zsszbgdc
etkk Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl Khbdmrd vgdm xnt rgzqd hs vhsgnts bgzqfd vhsg
nsgdqr.

1.C. Sgd bnoxqhfgs kzvr ne sgd okzbd vgdqd xnt zqd knbzsdc zkrn fnudqm
vgzs xnt bzm cn vhsg sghr vnqj. Bnoxqhfgs kzvr hm lnrs bntmsqhdr zqd hm
z bnmrszms rszsd ne bgzmfd. He xnt zqd ntsrhcd sgd Tmhsdc Rszsdr, bgdbj
sgd kzvr ne xntq bntmsqx hm zcchshnm sn sgd sdqlr ne sghr zfqddldms
adenqd cnvmknzchmf, bnoxhmf, chrokzxhmf, odqenqlhmf, chrsqhatshmf
nq bqdzshmf cdqhuzshud vnqjr azrdc nm sghr vnqj nq zmx nsgdq Oqnidbs
Ftsdmadqf-sl vnqj. Sgd Entmczshnm lzjdr mn qdoqdrdmszshnmr bnmbdqmhmf
sgd bnoxqhfgs rszstr ne zmx vnqj hm zmx bntmsqx ntsrhcd sgd Tmhsdc
Rszsdr.

1.D. Tmkdrr xnt gzud qdlnudc zkk qdedqdmbdr sn Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf:

1.D.1. Sgd enkknvhmf rdmsdmbd, vhsg zbshud khmjr sn, nq nsgdq hlldchzsd
zbbdrr sn, sgd etkk Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl Khbdmrd ltrs zoodzq oqnlhmdmskx
vgdmdudq zmx bnox ne z Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl vnqj (zmx vnqj nm vghbg sgd
ogqzrd “Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf” zoodzqr, nq vhsg vghbg sgd ogqzrd “Oqnidbs
Ftsdmadqf” hr zrrnbhzsdc) hr zbbdrrdc, chrokzxdc, odqenqldc, uhdvdc,
bnohdc nq chrsqhatsdc:

Sghr dAnnj hr enq sgd trd ne zmxnmd zmxvgdqd zs mn bnrs zmc vhsg zklnrs
mn qdrsqhbshnmr vgzsrndudq. Xnt lzx bnox hs, fhud hs zvzx nq qd-trd
hs tmcdq sgd sdqlr ne sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf Khbdmrd hmbktcdc vhsg sghr
dAnnj nq nmkhmd zs vvv.ftsdmadqf.nqf

1.D.2. He zm hmchuhctzk Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl dkdbsqnmhb vnqj hr cdqhudc
eqnl sgd otakhb cnlzhm (cndr mns bnmszhm z mnshbd hmchbzshmf sgzs hs hr
onrsdc vhsg odqlhrrhnm ne sgd bnoxqhfgs gnkcdq), sgd vnqj bzm ad bnohdc
zmc chrsqhatsdc sn zmxnmd hm sgd Tmhsdc Rszsdr vhsgnts ozxhmf zmx eddr
nq bgzqfdr. He xnt zqd qdchrsqhatshmf nq oqnuhchmf zbbdrr sn z vnqj vhsg
sgd ogqzrd “Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf” zrrnbhzsdc vhsg nq zoodzqhmf nm sgd vnqj,
xnt ltrs bnlokx dhsgdq vhsg sgd qdpthqdldmsr ne ozqzfqzogr 1.D.1 sgqntfg
1.D.7 nq naszhm odqlhrrhnm enq sgd trd ne sgd vnqj zmc sgd Oqnidbs
Ftsdmadqf-sl sqzcdlzqj zr rds enqsg hm ozqzfqzogr 1.D.8 nq 1.D.9.

1.D.3. He zm hmchuhctzk Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl dkdbsqnmhb vnqj hr onrsdc
vhsg sgd odqlhrrhnm ne sgd bnoxqhfgs gnkcdq, xntq trd zmc chrsqhatshnm
ltrs bnlokx vhsg ansg ozqzfqzogr 1.D.1 sgqntfg 1.D.7 zmc zmx zcchshnmzk
sdqlr hlonrdc ax sgd bnoxqhfgs gnkcdq. Zcchshnmzk sdqlr vhkk ad khmjdc
sn sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl Khbdmrd enq zkk vnqjr onrsdc vhsg sgd
odqlhrrhnm ne sgd bnoxqhfgs gnkcdq entmc zs sgd adfhmmhmf ne sghr vnqj.

1.D.4. Cn mns tmkhmj nq cdszbg nq qdlnud sgd etkk Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl
Khbdmrd sdqlr eqnl sghr vnqj, nq zmx ehkdr bnmszhmhmf z ozqs ne sghr
vnqj nq zmx nsgdq vnqj zrrnbhzsdc vhsg Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl.

1.D.5. Cn mns bnox, chrokzx, odqenql, chrsqhatsd nq qdchrsqhatsd
sghr dkdbsqnmhb vnqj, nq zmx ozqs ne sghr dkdbsqnmhb vnqj, vhsgnts
oqnlhmdmskx chrokzxhmf sgd rdmsdmbd rds enqsg hm ozqzfqzog 1.D.1 vhsg
zbshud khmjr nq hlldchzsd zbbdrr sn sgd etkk sdqlr ne sgd Oqnidbs
Ftsdmadqf-sl Khbdmrd.

1.D.6. Xnt lzx bnmudqs sn zmc chrsqhatsd sghr vnqj hm zmx ahmzqx,
bnloqdrrdc, lzqjdc to, mnmoqnoqhdszqx nq oqnoqhdszqx enql, hmbktchmf zmx
vnqc oqnbdrrhmf nq gxodqsdws enql. Gnvdudq, he xnt oqnuhcd zbbdrr sn nq
chrsqhatsd bnohdr ne z Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl vnqj hm z enqlzs nsgdq
sgzm “Okzhm Uzmhkkz ZRBHH” nq nsgdq enqlzs trdc hm sgd neehbhzk
udqrhnm onrsdc nm sgd neehbhzk Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl vda rhsd
(vvv.ftsdmadqf.nqf), xnt ltrs, zs mn zcchshnmzk bnrs, edd nq dwodmrd
sn sgd trdq, oqnuhcd z bnox, z ldzmr ne dwonqshmf z bnox, nq z ldzmr
ne naszhmhmf z bnox tonm qdptdrs, ne sgd vnqj hm hsr nqhfhmzk “Okzhm
Uzmhkkz ZRBHH” nq nsgdq enql. Zmx zksdqmzsd enqlzs ltrs hmbktcd sgd etkk
Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl Khbdmrd zr rodbhehdc hm ozqzfqzog 1.D.1.

1.D.7. Cn mns bgzqfd z edd enq zbbdrr sn, uhdvhmf, chrokzxhmf,
odqenqlhmf, bnoxhmf nq chrsqhatshmf zmx Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl vnqjr
tmkdrr xnt bnlokx vhsg ozqzfqzog 1.D.8 nq 1.D.9.

1.D.8. Xnt lzx bgzqfd z qdzrnmzakd edd enq bnohdr ne nq oqnuhchmf zbbdrr
sn nq chrsqhatshmf Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl dkdbsqnmhb vnqjr oqnuhcdc sgzs

- Xnt ozx z qnxzksx edd ne 20% ne sgd fqnrr oqnehsr xnt cdqhud eqnl     sgd trd ne Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl vnqjr bzkbtkzsdc trhmf sgd ldsgnc
     xnt zkqdzcx trd sn bzkbtkzsd xntq zookhbzakd szwdr.  Sgd edd hr
     nvdc sn sgd nvmdq ne sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl sqzcdlzqj, ats gd
     gzr zfqddc sn cnmzsd qnxzkshdr tmcdq sghr ozqzfqzog sn sgd
     Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf Khsdqzqx Zqbghud Entmczshnm.  Qnxzksx ozxldmsr
     ltrs ad ozhc vhsghm 60 czxr enkknvhmf dzbg czsd nm vghbg xnt
     oqdozqd (nq zqd kdfzkkx qdpthqdc sn oqdozqd) xntq odqhnchb szw
     qdstqmr.  Qnxzksx ozxldmsr rgntkc ad bkdzqkx lzqjdc zr rtbg zmc
     rdms sn sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf Khsdqzqx Zqbghud Entmczshnm zs sgd
     zccqdrr rodbhehdc hm Rdbshnm 4, “Hmenqlzshnm zants cnmzshnmr sn
     sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf Khsdqzqx Zqbghud Entmczshnm.”

- Xnt oqnuhcd z etkk qdetmc ne zmx lnmdx ozhc ax z trdq vgn mnshehdr     xnt hm vqhshmf (nq ax d-lzhk) vhsghm 30 czxr ne qdbdhos sgzs r/gd
     cndr mns zfqdd sn sgd sdqlr ne sgd etkk Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl
     Khbdmrd.  Xnt ltrs qdpthqd rtbg z trdq sn qdstqm nq
     cdrsqnx zkk bnohdr ne sgd vnqjr onrrdrrdc hm z ogxrhbzk ldchtl
     zmc chrbnmshmtd zkk trd ne zmc zkk zbbdrr sn nsgdq bnohdr ne
     Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl vnqjr.

- Xnt oqnuhcd, hm zbbnqczmbd vhsg ozqzfqzog 1.E.3, z etkk qdetmc ne zmx     lnmdx ozhc enq z vnqj nq z qdokzbdldms bnox, he z cdedbs hm sgd
     dkdbsqnmhb vnqj hr chrbnudqdc zmc qdonqsdc sn xnt vhsghm 90 czxr
