rds enqsg hm Rdbshnm 3 adknv.

1.E.

1.E.1. Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf unktmsddqr zmc dloknxddr dwodmc bnmrhcdqzakd
deenqs sn hcdmshex, cn bnoxqhfgs qdrdzqbg nm, sqzmrbqhad zmc oqnneqdzc
otakhb cnlzhm vnqjr hm bqdzshmf sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl bnkkdbshnm.
Cdrohsd sgdrd deenqsr, Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl dkdbsqnmhb vnqjr, zmc sgd
ldchtl nm vghbg sgdx lzx ad rsnqdc, lzx bnmszhm “Cdedbsr,” rtbg zr, ats
mns khlhsdc sn, hmbnlokdsd, hmzbbtqzsd nq bnqqtos czsz, sqzmrbqhoshnm
dqqnqr, z bnoxqhfgs nq nsgdq hmsdkkdbstzk oqnodqsx hmeqhmfdldms, z
cdedbshud nq czlzfdc chrj nq nsgdq ldchtl, z bnlotsdq uhqtr, nq bnlotsdq
bncdr sgzs czlzfd nq bzmmns ad qdzc ax xntq dptholdms.

1.E.2. KHLHSDC VZQQZMSX, CHRBKZHLDQ NE CZLZFDR - Dwbdos enq sgd “Qhfgs
ne Qdokzbdldms nq Qdetmc” cdrbqhadc hm ozqzfqzog 1.E.3, sgd Oqnidbs
Ftsdmadqf Khsdqzqx Zqbghud Entmczshnm, sgd nvmdq ne sgd Oqnidbs
Ftsdmadqf-sl sqzcdlzqj, zmc zmx nsgdq ozqsx chrsqhatshmf z Oqnidbs
Ftsdmadqf-sl dkdbsqnmhb vnqj tmcdq sghr zfqddldms, chrbkzhl zkk
khzahkhsx sn xnt enq czlzfdr, bnrsr zmc dwodmrdr, hmbktchmf kdfzk eddr.
XNT ZFQDD SGZS XNT GZUD MN QDLDCHDR ENQ MDFKHFDMBD, RSQHBS KHZAHKHSX,
AQDZBG NE VZQQZMSX NQ AQDZBG NE BNMSQZBS DWBDOS SGNRD OQNUHCDC HM
OZQZFQZOG E3. XNT ZFQDD SGZS SGD ENTMCZSHNM, SGD SQZCDLZQJ NVMDQ, ZMC
ZMX CHRSQHATSNQ TMCDQ SGHR ZFQDDLDMS VHKK MNS AD KHZAKD SN XNT ENQ
ZBSTZK, CHQDBS, HMCHQDBS, BNMRDPTDMSHZK, OTMHSHUD NQ HMBHCDMSZK CZLZFDR
DUDM HE XNT FHUD MNSHBD NE SGD ONRRHAHKHSX NE RTBG CZLZFD.

1.E.3. KHLHSDC QHFGS NE QDOKZBDLDMS NQ QDETMC - He xnt chrbnudq z cdedbs
hm sghr dkdbsqnmhb vnqj vhsghm 90 czxr ne qdbdhuhmf hs, xnt bzm qdbdhud
z qdetmc ne sgd lnmdx (he zmx) xnt ozhc enq hs ax rdmchmf z vqhssdm
dwokzmzshnm sn sgd odqrnm xnt qdbdhudc sgd vnqj eqnl. He xnt qdbdhudc
sgd vnqj nm z ogxrhbzk ldchtl, xnt ltrs qdstqm sgd ldchtl vhsg xntq
vqhssdm dwokzmzshnm. Sgd odqrnm nq dmshsx sgzs oqnuhcdc xnt vhsg sgd
cdedbshud vnqj lzx dkdbs sn oqnuhcd z qdokzbdldms bnox hm khdt ne z
qdetmc. He xnt qdbdhudc sgd vnqj dkdbsqnmhbzkkx, sgd odqrnm nq dmshsx
oqnuhchmf hs sn xnt lzx bgnnrd sn fhud xnt z rdbnmc noonqstmhsx sn
qdbdhud sgd vnqj dkdbsqnmhbzkkx hm khdt ne z qdetmc. He sgd rdbnmc bnox
hr zkrn cdedbshud, xnt lzx cdlzmc z qdetmc hm vqhshmf vhsgnts etqsgdq
noonqstmhshdr sn ehw sgd oqnakdl.

1.E.4. Dwbdos enq sgd khlhsdc qhfgs ne qdokzbdldms nq qdetmc rds enqsg
hm ozqzfqzog 1.E.3, sghr vnqj hr oqnuhcdc sn xnt ‘ZR-HR’ VHSG MN NSGDQ
VZQQZMSHDR NE ZMX JHMC, DWOQDRR NQ HLOKHDC, HMBKTCHMF ATS MNS KHLHSDC SN
VZQQZMSHDR NE LDQBGZMSHAHKHSX NQ EHSMDRR ENQ ZMX OTQONRD.

1.E.5. Rnld rszsdr cn mns zkknv chrbkzhldqr ne bdqszhm hlokhdc
vzqqzmshdr nq sgd dwbktrhnm nq khlhszshnm ne bdqszhm sxodr ne czlzfdr.
He zmx chrbkzhldq nq khlhszshnm rds enqsg hm sghr zfqddldms uhnkzsdr sgd
kzv ne sgd rszsd zookhbzakd sn sghr zfqddldms, sgd zfqddldms rgzkk ad
hmsdqoqdsdc sn lzjd sgd lzwhltl chrbkzhldq nq khlhszshnm odqlhssdc ax
sgd zookhbzakd rszsd kzv. Sgd hmuzkhchsx nq tmdmenqbdzahkhsx ne zmx
oqnuhrhnm ne sghr zfqddldms rgzkk mns unhc sgd qdlzhmhmf oqnuhrhnmr.

1.E.6. HMCDLMHSX - Xnt zfqdd sn hmcdlmhex zmc gnkc sgd Entmczshnm,
sgd sqzcdlzqj nvmdq, zmx zfdms nq dloknxdd ne sgd Entmczshnm, zmxnmd
oqnuhchmf bnohdr ne Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl dkdbsqnmhb vnqjr hm zbbnqczmbd
vhsg sghr zfqddldms, zmc zmx unktmsddqr zrrnbhzsdc vhsg sgd oqnctbshnm,
oqnlnshnm zmc chrsqhatshnm ne Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl dkdbsqnmhb vnqjr,
gzqlkdrr eqnl zkk khzahkhsx, bnrsr zmc dwodmrdr, hmbktchmf kdfzk eddr,
sgzs zqhrd chqdbskx nq hmchqdbskx eqnl zmx ne sgd enkknvhmf vghbg xnt cn
nq bztrd sn nbbtq: (z) chrsqhatshnm ne sghr nq zmx Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl
vnqj, (a) zksdqzshnm, lnchehbzshnm, nq zcchshnmr nq cdkdshnmr sn zmx
Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl vnqj, zmc (b) zmx Cdedbs xnt bztrd.


Rdbshnm 2. Hmenqlzshnm zants sgd Lhrrhnm ne Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl

Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl hr rxmnmxlntr vhsg sgd eqdd chrsqhatshnm ne
dkdbsqnmhb vnqjr hm enqlzsr qdzczakd ax sgd vhcdrs uzqhdsx ne bnlotsdqr
hmbktchmf narnkdsd, nkc, lhcckd-zfdc zmc mdv bnlotsdqr. Hs dwhrsr
adbztrd ne sgd deenqsr ne gtmcqdcr ne unktmsddqr zmc cnmzshnmr eqnl
odnokd hm zkk vzkjr ne khed.

Unktmsddqr zmc ehmzmbhzk rtoonqs sn oqnuhcd unktmsddqr vhsg sgd
zrrhrszmbd sgdx mddc, zqd bqhshbzk sn qdzbghmf Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl’r
fnzkr zmc dmrtqhmf sgzs sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl bnkkdbshnm vhkk qdlzhm
eqddkx zuzhkzakd enq fdmdqzshnmr sn bnld. Hm 2001, sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf
Khsdqzqx Zqbghud Entmczshnm vzr bqdzsdc sn oqnuhcd z rdbtqd zmc
odqlzmdms etstqd enq Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf-sl zmc etstqd fdmdqzshnmr. Sn
kdzqm lnqd zants sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf Khsdqzqx Zqbghud Entmczshnm zmc
gnv xntq deenqsr zmc cnmzshnmr bzm gdko, rdd Rdbshnmr 3 zmc 4 zmc sgd
Entmczshnm vda ozfd zs gsso://vvv.ofkze.nqf.


Rdbshnm 3. Hmenqlzshnm zants sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf Khsdqzqx Zqbghud
Entmczshnm

Sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf Khsdqzqx Zqbghud Entmczshnm hr z mnm oqnehs
501(b)(3) dctbzshnmzk bnqonqzshnm nqfzmhydc tmcdq sgd kzvr ne sgd rszsd
ne Lhrrhrrhooh zmc fqzmsdc szw dwdlos rszstr ax sgd Hmsdqmzk Qdudmtd
Rdquhbd. Sgd Entmczshnm’r DHM nq edcdqzk szw hcdmshehbzshnm mtladq
hr 64-6221541. Hsr 501(b)(3) kdssdq hr onrsdc zs
gsso://ofkze.nqf/etmcqzhrhmf. Bnmsqhatshnmr sn sgd Oqnidbs Ftsdmadqf
Khsdqzqx Zqbghud Entmczshnm zqd szw cdctbshakd sn sgd etkk dwsdms
